wder<br>1½ tsp bicarbonate of soda<br>½ tsp sea salt flakes, plus extra for sprinkling<br>110g/3¾oz unsalted butter, diced and at room temperature<br>350g/12½oz caster sugar<br>110g/3¾oz caster sugar<br>2 free-range eggs<br>2 tsp vanilla extract<br>200g/7oz plain chocolate'),(16,'Greek Salad','Fresh salad with tomatoes, cucumbers, olives, and feta cheese','Salad','Appetizer','Greece',15,'Easy','Chop vegetables; Toss with olives and feta; Drizzle with dressing',_binary 'media/meal/Greek Salad.jpg',4,'4 skinless, boneless chicken breasts<br>4 tbsp ready-made tikka masala curry paste<br>2 tbsp natural yoghurt<br>3 tbsp vegetable oil or ghee (clarified butter)<br>1 cinnamon stick<br>8 cardamom pods<br>1 large onion, finely chopped<br>3cm/1¼in piece of fresh ginger, peeled and finely grated<br>2 garlic cloves, crushed<br>1 tsp ground cumin<br>1 tsp ground coriander<br>½ tsp ground turmeric<br>½–1 tsp cayenne pepper (depending on how hot you like it)<br>half a 400g can chopped tomatoes<br>150ml/5fl oz chicken stock or water<br>1½ tsp garam masala<br>½ lemon, juice only<br>½ tsp salt'),(17,'Pancakes','Fluffy breakfast pancakes served with syrup or toppings','Cake','dessert','Various',20,'Easy','Mix batter; Cook on griddle',_binary 'media/meal/Pancakes.jpg',4,'½ tbsp olive oil<br>75g/2½ oz pancetta, chopped<br>200g/7oz dried spaghetti<br>2 large free-range eggs<br>100g/3½oz Parmesan, grated, plus extra for serving<br>1 tbsp full-fat milk<br>salt and freshly ground pepper<br>'),(18,'Chicken Parmesan','Breaded and fried chicken topped with marinara sauce and cheese','Meat','Main Course','Italy',45,'Intermediate','Bread and fry chicken; Top with sauce and cheese; Bake',_binary 'media/meal/chicken-parmesan.jpg',3,'4 skinless, boneless chicken breasts<br>4 tbsp ready-made tikka masala curry paste<br>2 tbsp natural yoghurt<br>3 tbsp vegetable oil or ghee (clarified butter)<br>1 cinnamon stick<br>8 cardamom pods<br>1 large onion, finely chopped<br>3cm/1¼in piece of fresh ginger, p